Questions for tasks are based on HTMLQuestion. An implementation based on QuestionForm
was also attempted. However, QuestionForm is limiting with respect to presentation
of questions. HTMLQuestion is based on:
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSMechTurk/latest/AWSMturkAPI/ApiReference_HTMLQuestionArticle.html

Creating questions based on a .question file:
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSMechTurk/latest/AWSMturkAPI/ApiReference_QuestionFormDataStructureArticle.html

Input files have to be tab delimited rather than comma separated.

Review policies can be used to automatically score an assignment or check agreement
on several answers to a hit:
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSMechTurk/latest/AWSMturkAPI/ApiReference_ReviewPoliciesArticle.html
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSMechTurk/latest/AWSMturkAPI/ApiReference_AssignmentReviewPolicies.html
http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSMechTurk/latest/AWSMturkAPI/ApiReference_HITReviewPolicies.html